HEADWORD: Spinage
<hw>Spin"age</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(?)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>espinache</ets>, <ets>espinoche</ets>, F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧pinard</ets>; cf. F. <ets>spinace</ets>, Sp.
